data.description: This beautiful 3-bed, 2-bath home nestled within a secure gated community offers both comfort & security - upon stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious & inviting living area, adorned with large windows that allow an abundance of natural light to fill the space - the open floor plan effortlessly connects the living room & kitchen, making it perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quality time with family - the chef's kitchen features sleek countertops, stainless appliances, & ample storage space - the three bedrooms in this home offer comfortable retreats for relaxation - the primary suite is a private oasis, complete with a generously sized bedroom, a walk-in closet, & an ensuite bathroom - the additional two bedrooms are equally inviting & spacious, with ample closet space & easy access to the second bathroom - outside, the home extends its charm with a well-manicured backyard, providing the perfect space to enjoy a morning coffee on the patio or host a summer barbecue!
